<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">م ح ا:</span> <span class="c2">(مَحَا)</span> لَوْحَهُ مِنْ بَابِ عَدَا وَرَمَى وَيَمْحَاهُ أَيْضًا <span class="c2">(مَحْيًا)</span> فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(مَمْحُوٌّ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(مَمْحِيٌّ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(امَّحَى)</span> انْفَعَلَ مِنْهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(امْتَحَى)</span> لُغَةٌ فِيهِ ضَعِيفَةٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>